                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Chargé d’Affaires</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-10-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 8, 1912</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Though not yet officially informed, I learn that Maza was sentenced yesterday to
                    two years and six months imprisonment. The prosecution had asked for four years
                    and two months.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gibson</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
